Justine went into the town very early the next morning.  She went to the market and purchased the finest fruits she could find. She also purchased a basket to place them in. There was a lot to choose from since Capt Merlobo had returned with his fleet.<br>
She went home and walked about her garden picking the finest flowers there.  Going into the kitchen, she arranged the basket of fruits and flowers into an array. Going to her desk, she sat and penned a note.::<br>
My dearest friends:<br>
Word cannot explain how sorry I am to miss our dinner last night.  Duties were overwhelming and I just lost track of time.  Please forgive me.<br>
I hope this basket is enjoyable to you both.  And I shall be by the Inn at 9 AM to take you both for breakfast and show you around the Island.  I know you are anxious to return to your home, but allow me one more day to be with you both.<br>
See you in a few hours.<br>
Justine<br>
::Justine placed the note on the handle of the basket, tying it with a violet ribbon.  She carried it down to the Inn instructing the deskclerk to bring this to Hipp's room around 8 AM.  Then she ran back to the cabin to dress properly, take care of Dabriel and Fhad.  She hoped that the ladies forgave her.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/BC.html BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/15/00 4:46 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/Hippolyte?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Next Morning </span><hr size=1> ::Hipp woke with the sun peaking in thru the window to her room.  She had quickly fell asleep in the soft bed, the night before.  But, the smells from outside and the sun awoke her senses.  She quickly dressed and brushed her auburn hair.  She grabbed a purple silk chamise, belted it with her golden belt and then quickly ran out to the barn and checked upon Monsoon.  After nuzzling the mare, she found a brush hanging on the stall wall and lovingly brushed the mare.  <br>
After spending needed time with the mare, she returned to her room.  There she found the basket of flowers and fruit.  She smiled at the site of the food and quickly grabbed a string of grapes.  Then noticed the note.  She read it as best she could, english still so foreign to her.  But, she managed to make out what Justine was tgrying to say.  She quickly tossed some grapes in her mouth.  And then walked over to the water basin by the mirror.  It had been refreshed with clean water and two fresh, dry soft white cloth lay beside it.  Hipp pulled off her chamise, now covered in horse hair and threw it into an open saddle bag.  She grabbed a clothe and wet it.  Then washing her body as best she could.:: I am going to have to find a lake or stream and do this right :: she rolls her eyes at cleaning like this.  Then finishes and again brushes her hair.  She bent down to a saddle bag and looked for new clothes. She found a new clean silk garment and threw it over her head, then belted her golden belt around it. Then placed her scabbard and scimitar to another leather belt at her waist.  As she walked to the door..she reached out and pulled her Queen's cape from a hook on the wall.. and unceremoniously throwing it over her shoulder.  She knocked upon Sethra's door:: Hey!  Yaasooooo.. Sethra.  I will meet you down stairs at the tavern. :: After hearing a endaksi/okay from inside....she walked to the tavern.  She found a seat near a window and sat down.  A wench came and brought Hippolyte her favorite wine..which made the amazon queen smirk.  She waved her hands and asked the queen for something warm to drink and eat.  The woman smiled, left and then brought back some coffee.  Hipp raised an eyebrow and then sipped it.:: Ah... kala!  ::The amazon queen contented drank the coffee and watched the people pass by outside the window.  After a bit, the wench brought back Queen Hippolyte two plates heaped with food.  Hipp smiled and began to eat.  She thought, ohhh how it tasted sooo good.  Then as she ate and drank..she went back to her people watching out the window.:::: <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ujustineash.showPublicProfile?language=EN>JustineAsh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/15/00 8:11 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Next Morning </span><hr size=1> ::Justine didn't want to be late today.  She kissed Dabby, Fhad and slapped Anna on her rump playfully and ran out the door and down the hill to the Inn.  She stopped at the door to fix her hair which was windblown about her, pinning her hair up into a ponytail.  <br>
She opened the door and went inside, giving her eyes a few moments to adjust to the darkness from the bright sun.  She smiled as she saw the Queen and the large plates of food before her.  She was glad that the InnKeeper was taking care of her guests so well.  <br>
Justine walked over to her and trying to remember the gestures, she saluted the Queen as the Queen had done to Justine when she first arrived.::<br>
I hope I did that right Hipp.  I've been practicing.  Was it good or as really bad as I felt it was?<br>
::Justine chuckled taking a seat across from her.  The serving wench slipping a cup of coffee in front of her.  The wench made sure that the Queen still had enough food before slipping away from the table.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Sethra</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/16/00 8:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The morning</span><hr size=1> :: Sethra fell back asleep after Hipp had woken her up. She slowly wakes up and realizes how late it was and how her Queen was waiting for her. She goes and cleans up and changes and head out the door running for the tarvern.She gets there and sees JustineAsh sitting across from Hipp. She thinks to herself..Great I am late... she stops so she can catch her breath then walks over &quot;Yasoo. Sorry I am late.&quot; She sits down beside Hipp, hoping no one is mad. :: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ujustineash.showPublicProfile?language=EN>JustineAsh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/16/00 9:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The morning</span><hr size=1> ::Justine sat across from Hipp watching her eat and sipping her coffee.  She looked to her left and saw Sethra standing there.  She smiled warmly to her.::  Good Morning Sethra.  Come join us for some breakfast and then I want to take you around and show you the town.  Is there anything special you want?  <br>
::The serving wench appeared silently beside her and waited for a reply:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/BC.html BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/16/00 5:09 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/Hippolyte?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The morning</span><hr size=1> ::she smiles seeing Justine salute to her and salutes back:: ahh that is very good!  :::smirks:: we will make an amazon out of you yet!  ::chuckles and then looks to see Sethra:: Yasoo Sethra, don't worry about it.  We may have a full day ahead of us. ::then she looks to Justine:: I look forward to seeing a bit more of your village today and signing of our alliance scroll.  ::sighs:: As wonderful as it is here.  I would like to be able to get back on the road in the morning.  I do miss my family and athelfi in Themiscrya very much.  I am not used to being away from them for so long. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Sethra</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/17/00 7:03 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RE: The Morning</span><hr size=1> :: Sethra smiles and starts eating what the wench brought her. She drank some water and finished up while Hipp and Justine spoke. &quot; I wouldn't mind visiting the merchants. I'm sure they have some neat stuff I can bring home.&quot; She smiles. She asks the wench to re-fill her glass of water, she was very thirsty. After she finishes, she sits patiently and waits for Hipp and justine to finshe. She couldn't wait to look at the village.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=61&stop=67>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showPrevMessage?topicID=7.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showNextMessage?topicID=7.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.threadControl?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="C